  "tab-travel": "Cinematic travel and lifestyle photography showcasing the natural beauty of the Isle of Wight and global destinations. <br><br> Utilising high-end ground and aerial drone videography, I produce compelling Isle of Wight tourism imagery. I have partnered with major local organisations such as Wightlink and the NHS to promote Island tourism and create engaging recruitment campaigns that highlight the unique coastal lifestyle. <br><br> Beyond local shores, my portfolio includes working with renowned global tourism brands like Sunsail and Topdeck, capturing premium lifestyle imagery and dynamic travel content across the world.",
