  "tab-video-travel": "Immersive 4K drone and ground videography tailored for Isle of Wight tourism boards, local resorts, and commercial campaigns. <br><br> I've shot local tourism and recruitment campaigns for Wightlink and the Isle of Wight NHS Trust, and travelled further afield to capture video content for Sunsail and Topdeck. <br><br> Whether it’s aerial drone footage or ground-level storytelling, I focus on creating videos that naturally capture the feel of a destination.",
  "tab-video-music": "Music videos and live performance videography for Isle of Wight musicians, bands, and touring artists.",
  "tab-video-shorts": "Cinematic short film production and directing, utilising Isle of Wight locations and visual storytelling. <br><br> I regularly collaborate with the production company Deadman where we received support from the Mike Howley Trust to help bring local stories to the screen. <br><br> These projects have picked up a few laurels along the way, including a category win at Montreal Independent Film Festival, alongside finalist spots and official selections at Brighton Rocks and Barnes.",
  "tab-video-theatre": "Engaging promotional video trailers and live performance recordings for Isle of Wight theatre companies and dance academies. <br><br> I have worked closely with Deadman on their nationally touring play, The Freshwater Five, by creating proof-of-concept and R&D videos to help them market the show and secure Arts Council funding. <br><br> Alongside promotional trailers, I shoot full live performance recordings, such as an end-of-term shows for the Joel Morris Dance Academy.",
  "tab-web-branding": "Bespoke website and poster design, alongside cohesive brand identity creation for Isle of Wight businesses. <br><br> On the digital side, I design, build, and maintain custom websites, including my own portfolio and the official site for the production company Deadman C.I.C. <br><br> For print and digital marketing, I design advertising materials in all required sizes, often exclusively incorporating my own photography. Recent work includes creating advertising campaigns for local holiday lets and designing promotional posters for the Abbeyfield Society in Shanklin to help advertise their available spaces. <br><br> To ensure a seamless process for my clients, I liaise directly with the publications where the ads will run to confirm correct dimensions and make any necessary design adjustments for maximum effect.",
  "tab-floor-plans": "Highly accurate 2D and 3D architectural floor plans for Isle of Wight real estate listings and property developments. <br><br> I provide detailed, standard floor plans for everyday property sales and lettings. For more complex projects, I use Rayon to create precise, to-scale drawings ideal for properties undergoing renovation, commercial space refits, and interior design planning. <br><br> Whether it is a simple layout for an estate agent or a comprehensive spatial map for a development pitch, I deliver clear and professional assets.",
